{"tid":437150,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel 終於追上IBM：成功研發17量子位元CPU","createTime":"2017-10-15T17:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T06:33:38.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"26fab2d9df5215f821cd64e4a14d7f40d120f356","tid":437150,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:19:07.000Z","msg":"量子運算將會是未來電腦發展的重心，一眾高科技廠商都爭相研發下一代超級電腦所用到的技術。Intel 最新發佈了他們的 17-QUBIT 超導體測試晶片，現時正配合其他硬件，進行系統測試。他們的晶片將會提供給荷蘭量子運算研究機構 QuTech 作測試與研究用途。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/00-1-1-768x432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F00-1-1-768x432.jpg&h=9b1c1240&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n在 5 月 IBM 曾發表了首個 17-QUBIT  處理器晶片設計，而 Google 在 4 月也發佈了 9-QUBIT 處理器晶片的研究成果。Intel 在量子運算技術上亦踏前一步，成功開發了這枚具有 17 個量子位元處理器的晶片，能匹敵之前 IBM 的量子運算晶片。此晶片具有可擴充的設計，相比起傳統晶片，訊號的吞吐量可以提升 10 倍至 100 倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。高運算能力的量子運算，可作科學研究用途，例如研製新藥物時模擬分子結構。<br />\n<br />\nIntel 稱每個量子位元都相當脆弱，處理器只能在比太空環境冷 250 倍的環境下運作，因此晶片使用了超導體材料製作而成，以及要有特殊的封裝技術，避免數據受到干擾而流失。<br />\n<br />\nIntel 與 Google 的最終目標，是研製出具有 49 個量子位元處理器的晶片，運算能力有望超越所有超級電腦。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/b01-1-768x512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fb01-1-768x512.jpg&h=c36756e8&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qEvrPYmvBIY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqEvrPYmvBIY&d=Qn7MYfq1I5E%2F%2Fjqkniha%2BG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=20b45170\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qEvrPYmvBIY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/10/12/intel17qubitchips/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2Fintel17qubitchips%2Flife-tech%2F&d=Qn7MYfq1I5E%2F%2Fjqkniha%2BG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a5130ada\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/10/12/intel17qubitchips/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"a4fc2991bd9a477015b0059b9ff538fe9604b63b","tid":437150,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:20:50.000Z","msg":"Intel、Google 好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！！<br />\n<br />\n想知 AMD 又有冇研發緊呢啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6f3774ece2159d64d7f3576e674bedd4373ca1","tid":437150,"uid":1696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:23:56.000Z","msg":"撚追到ibm<br />\n只要ibm想 隨時可以量產量子cpu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54d61cf51e6172d94c0f262073e23ab032ce9a6","tid":437150,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撚追到ibm<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只要ibm想 隨時可以量產量子cpu</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留名學嘢"},{"pid":"cf5ff4dbe1cc8c07d34743268b89dd71aa9e551d","tid":437150,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撚追到ibm<br />\n只要ibm想 隨時可以量產量子cpu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887fd9253845ab4b8df76c20a07fd1dd5b3db1ff","tid":437150,"uid":36421,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:37:45.000Z","msg":"比太空冷250倍即係幾凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絕對零度好似都係-273咋喎"},{"pid":"623104f761431a116617398a0d112b52d97cf13c","tid":437150,"uid":1696,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>撚追到ibm<br />\n只要ibm想 隨時可以量產量子cpu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIBM 好早已經玩緊量子cpu<br />\n佢賣x86嗰陣已經有足夠既技術玩量產初代量子cpu<br />\n發夢仲見到美國政府已經有幾部量子電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 由頭到尾都係到9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b69d9722aaa8ab29ba1856b4c06690034f2bf7","tid":437150,"uid":108421,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:40:01.000Z","msg":"高唔高科技唔想知<br />\n呢粒嘢睇到我密集恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73036627662d54f54d107917ad2861205c58a80","tid":437150,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:40:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比太空冷250倍即係幾凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絕對零度好似都係-273咋喎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5902914719546141e0a9578d773c9f724adc5c9e","tid":437150,"uid":43721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高唔高科技唔想知<br />\n呢粒嘢睇到我密集恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79084be2f2df2f1860de46c39cda843cca19273b","tid":437150,"uid":138233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T17:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高唔高科技唔想知<br />\n呢粒嘢睇到我密集恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11fabfc9ba098ed3773c2852bff40427f8fff45","tid":437150,"uid":49153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T20:14:48.00